g_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1130630/extras/9e5d6bdc663de4aac22cc8930a1fc91e.avif?t=1590105095\" width=616 height=600 /></span><br>使用六款专为龙之部落英雄定制的全新戒指，探索各种战法战略。<br><br><br><strong>全新护身符</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1130630/extras/cc33418deb3d2499460ad3546bafbfba.avif?t=1590105095\" width=616 height=600 /></span><br>将废墟护身符加入你的收藏。有了它，任意英雄都可以发觉自己内心的黑暗一面，成为阿门罗的下一位大反派。",
